📢 Cere Network x Hyperbridge Integration Update
🎯 Tomorrow evening Cere Network will be integrated with Hyperbridge's Testnet and will be ready for community testing!

🌉 This important milestone brings us one step closer to our mainnet integration. With this testnet release, you'll be able to experience and test the new bridge functionality firsthand. The integration process took a bit longer than initially anticipated, moving mainnet launch back.

⏳ Timeline Update:
- Tomorrow evening: Testnet bridge goes live
- Rest of the week: public testing
- Next week: switch to mainnet (pending successful testnet validation & smooth deployment on mainnet)

🔍 We encourage all community members to participate in testing the bridge on testnet. Your feedback will be invaluable in ensuring a smooth mainnet deployment.

⚡️ Need to bridge urgently?
If you need to bridge your funds out of mainnet onto Ethereum urgently, then we can assist you with a manual bridge request (pls submit before Sunday 19/01). You can submit your transfer request here: https://forms.gle/UihUeuvVLjGPy2SK6

🤝 Join us in testing tomorrow! Your participation helps strengthen the Cere Network ecosystem.

Stay tuned for more updates!
